La secziun colliada (#section7) duess neir renderada schi spert scu pussebel sainza stueir implementar danovamaintg elemaints cun JavaScript. Ia less simplamaintg aveir en documaint HTML extralong, pero las secziuns colliadas duessan neir renderadas schi spert scu pussebel. Cun HTML vess chegl da funcziunar.
Igl cuntign pudess uscheia neir strimo, ed alloura igl navigatour mettess tot igls <contents> ainten la <div>.
< div id = sec1></div>
< div id= sec2></div>
etc.
< div id = sec7>section 7...</div>
< contents for=sec1>section 1...</contents>
< contents for=sec2>section 2...</contents>
etc.
